    <title>修改 hexo 的字體設定 引用 Google Font 為外部字體</title>
    <link href="https://hawkchou14.github.io/2020/03/24/hexo-external-fonts/"/>
    <id>https://hawkchou14.github.io/2020/03/24/hexo-external-fonts/</id>
    <published>2020-03-24T01:05:26.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-03-26T22:17:12.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo NexT 已支援外部字型，目前以 google font 為來進行設置<br>由於剛開始使用的 NexT 與後來更新的版本不同，列出兩個版本的設定方式:</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="更新-NexT-7-x-的修改方式"><a href="#更新-NexT-7-x-的修改方式" class="headerlink" title="更新 NexT 7.x 的修改方式"></a>更新 NexT 7.x 的修改方式</h1><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">font:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Uri of fonts host, e.g. https://fonts.googleapis.com (Default).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 如果是 Google 就保留空白，否則會有問題</span></span><br><span class="line">  host:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font options:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `external: true` will load this font family from `host` above.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `family: Times New Roman`. Without any quotes.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `size: x.x`. Use `em` as unit. Default: 1 (16px)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Global font settings used for all elements inside &lt;body&gt;.</span></span><br><span class="line">  global:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 其他字型的設定也是相同方式進行設定, size: 可以為 1.2 (加大)</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for site title (.site-title).</span></span><br><span class="line">  title:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for headlines (&lt;h1&gt; to &lt;h6&gt;).</span></span><br><span class="line">  headings:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for posts (.post-body).</span></span><br><span class="line">  posts:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for &lt;code&gt; and code blocks.</span></span><br><span class="line">  codes:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Courier New</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="NexT-5-x-的修改方式"><a href="#NexT-5-x-的修改方式" class="headerlink" title="NexT 5.x 的修改方式"></a>NexT 5.x 的修改方式</h1><h2 id="修改字體"><a href="#修改字體" class="headerlink" title="修改字體"></a>修改字體</h2><p>修改配置文件中的參數<br>修改配置文件 _config.yml ，找到font將下列代碼中紅色的部分修改成綠色的部分即可。可以根據實際情況稍作修改！ 文件位置: <code>./themes/next/_config.yml</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">font:</span><br><span class="line">- <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">+ <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Uri of fonts host, e.g. //fonts.googleapis.com (Default).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Uri字體主機，例如//fonts.googleapis.com（默認）。</span></span><br><span class="line">+ host: https://fonts.loli.net</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font options:字體選項：</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `external: true` will load this font family from `host` above.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `family: Times New Roman`. Without any quotes.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `size: xx`. Use `px` as unit.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Global font settings used for all elements in &lt;body&gt;.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 用於&lt;body&gt;中所有元素的全局字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  global:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for Headlines (H1, H2, H3, H4, H5, H6).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 標題的字體設置（H1，H2，H3，H4，H5，H6）。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Fallback to `global` font settings.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 回退到`global`字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  headings:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for posts.帖子的字體設置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Fallback to `global` font settings.回退到`global`字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  posts:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for Logo.LOGO的字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Fallback to `global` font settings.回退到`global`字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  logo:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 修改配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">找到 theme 的base.styl文件，位置在 `themes/next/<span class="built_in">source</span>/css/_variables/base.styl`,然後修改設定如下</span><br><span class="line">``` bash </span><br><span class="line">-<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-chinese, monospace</span><br><span class="line">+<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-base, monospace</span><br><span class="line">-<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>), consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-chinese, monospace <span class="keyword">if</span> get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">+<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>), consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-base, monospace <span class="keyword">if</span> get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="自定義項目-設置字體大小"><a href="#自定義項目-設置字體大小" class="headerlink" title="自定義項目:設置字體大小"></a>自定義項目:設置字體大小</h2><p>修改字體 size, 文件位置:<code>./themes/next/source/css/_variables/base.styl</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// Font size</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$font</span>-size-base          = 18px //改成你想要的即可！</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="設置字體顏色"><a href="#設置字體顏色" class="headerlink" title="設置字體顏色"></a>設置字體顏色</h2><p>設定文件的內容顏色！ 文件位置: <code>./themes/next/source/css/_custom/custom.styl</code><br>//修改字體顏色</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: &lt;在這裡填上你想要的顏色，如：<span class="comment">#000&gt;; //別漏了分號！</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Reference:<br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e0c5d4d72222" target="_blank" rel="noopener">參考1 霸气龙先森</a><br><a href="https://jacksonleon.gitee.io/posts/1540132352.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">參考2</a><br><a href="http://dinghongkai.com/2017/12/19/Blog-development-6-Customized-Style-of-Writing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">參考3</a></p>]]></content>
    
